config BR2_PACKAGE_PANICOS_ES_THEME_ART_BOOK_NEXT
	bool "panicos-es-theme-art-book-next"
	depends on BR2_PACKAGE_PANICOS_EMULATIONSTATION
	help
	  Anthony Caccese's "Art Book Next" theme for EmulationStation.
	  This is the same theme ROCKNIX and Knulli ship as their default,
	  pinned to the same SHA ROCKNIX uses so the look matches what
	  users coming from those distros expect.

	  Out of the box ES has no theme installed; once this package is
	  in the squashfs ES auto-picks it on first run. Switch themes
	  later in ES → UI Settings → Theme Set if you ship more than one.

	  ROCKNIX trims out a handful of subthemes (artwork-circuit,
	  -classic, -nintendont, -noir, -outline) to save space on these
	  handhelds; we mirror that trim.
